    "body": "Some language (like Scala and Clojure) distinguishes _futures_ from _promises._ I'm unsure whether they should be distinguished in Rust, though.\n\n(Although Scala distinguishes them, [Scala's overview on future and promise](http://docs.scala-lang.org/overviews/core/futures.html) says \"Depending on the implementation, it may be the case that `p.future eq p`.\")\n",
