    "body": "I haven't looked at it in a while but I recall extra::future being pretty lame (and I wrote a lot of it), so it should probably be reconsidered from the ground up. Pipes provide a lot of the capabilities of futures so I feel like futures should be a small policy layer on top of pipes. I'm in favor of having a future/promise split.\n",
